      <title>贷款紧缩导致泰国汽车产量跌至三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/thai-auto-output-heading-for-three-year-low-on-tight-lending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国工业联合会表示，由于国内销量和海外出货量均下滑，预计今年泰国的乘用车和卡车产量将达到 150 万辆，为 2021 年疫情爆发以来的最低产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/thai-auto-output-heading-for-three-year-low-on-tight-lending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:31:57 GMT</pubDate>
